.SH NAME
hpt3x3_freeze \- DMA workaround
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" hpt3x3_freeze
.BI "(struct ata_port *ap "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ap" 12
port to freeze

When freezing an HPT3x3 we must stop any pending DMA before
writing to the control register or the chip will hang
